longBusinessSummary: Brilliant Future AB (publ) provides data-driven survey and action platforms for measuring customer and employee experience in Sweden and internationally. The company offers Brilliant Employee, a web-based solution that allows employees and managers to give feedback; and Brilliant Customer, a web-based solution for customer surveys. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
